commit.message:
Support the full kw_only option for dataclasses

Including kw_only on dataclasses.dataclass,
kw_only on individual fields, and the dataclasses.KW_ONLY
placeholder marker.

Part of https://github.com/cython/cython/issues/4303

Draft for the moment since proper testing will be enabled by
https://github.com/cython/cython/pull/4955
Remove one more bit of special casing
